---
title: Quick Chicken Tikka Masala with Basmati Rice & Herby Yoghurt
description: Bold masala paste coats tender diced chicken and greens in this quick and easy Indian-inspired dish! With a bit of help from the
yoghurt and mango chutney toppings, the aromas will make you want to dig in before this hits the table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-tikka-garlic-rice-63595ed2.jpg
